<%= form_for @challenge, :url => {:action => "update", :id => @challenge.id }, :html => { :id => "wizard2", :method => :put }, remote: true  do |f| %>
  <% if @challenge.errors.any? %>
    <div id="error_explanation">
      <h2><%= pluralize(@challenge.errors.count, "error") %> prohibited this challenge from being saved:</h2>

      <ul>
      <% @challenge.errors.full_messages.each do |msg| %>
        <li><%= msg %></li>
      <% end %>
      </ul>
    </div>
  <% end %>


<div id="challenge_view2" class="challenge_details" >
		<label for="description">Rad. Here's a draft badge for you.<p>Tell more about your course/challenge/project/experience. 1-5 paragraphs should do. (You can always edit this later.)</label></p>
        
		<%= f.label :description %><br />
		<%= f.text_area :description, :size => "50x4" %>
		
	<button type="button", onclick="challengeView3()", class="c_button" >Next</button>

</div>

<div id="challenge_view3" class="challenge_details" >
		<p>K! You're on your way!
			</p>
   			<label for="subject">Is this for a specific academic Subject? (It's cool if you don't have one.)</label>
			
			<%= f.select( "subject", options_for_select(Subject.all.collect {|p| [ p.name, p.id ] }),:prompt => 'Select Subject' ) %>
			
	<button type="button", onclick="challengeView4()", class="c_button" >Next</button>

</div>

<div id="challenge_view4" class="challenge_details" >
<label for="needs">What will you need for this challenge? <p>Is it an online class? A series of experiments? What will you need to buy or borrow or beg?</p> 
	<p>Who or what type of people will you need to get help from?(Again, you can change this later).</p> </label>
			  <br >
			  
            <%= f.text_area :needs, :size => "50x4" %>
<button type="button", onclick="challengeView5()", class="c_button" >Next</button> 
</div>

<div id="challenge_view5" class="challenge_details" >
<label for="goal">Next-to-Last item! <p>List specific goals you'll need to achieve.<p>

<p class="smaller"> You'll perhaps make these more detailed in your plan; or maybe your goals are simply "Get A in online course." 
</p>
<p class="smaller">Or maybe you'll need to complete 4 of 6 badges in a series.<p>
<p class="smaller">This is just to get you thinking. You can change it all later.</p> 
<p class="smaller">Who or what type of people will you need to get help from?(Again, you can change this later).</p> </label>
			  
		
		<%= f.text_area :goal, :size => "50x4" %>
<button type="button", onclick="challengeView6()", class="c_button" >Next</button> 
</div>


<div id="challenge_view6" class="challenge_details" >
<label for="teacher">One and you're done. <p>Who will decide if you succeeded? </p>

<p>A teacher, counselor, or administrator at your school must give the final OK. Have you thought about who?<p>
<p></p> 
</label>
			  <br > 

		<%= f.text_area :teacher, :size => "30x2" %>    
		
		
		<%= f.submit %>
		<% end %>
</div>	

<div id="challenge_view_done" class="challenge_details" >
Congrats. You've got a CF concept!<p>Here's your draft badge:</p>

<div id="badge_holder_2">

</div>
</div>

<div id="challenge_next" class="challenge_details" >

</div>	